WEBVTT

00:14.160 --> 00:14.960
Your Majesty,

00:15.560 --> 00:18.160
this is the divorce agreement
between Young Lady Xie and me.

00:18.160 --> 00:20.640
The bond between her and me ends here.

00:22.390 --> 00:23.720
This is for your review.

00:38.350 --> 00:39.150
Your Majesty.

00:40.150 --> 00:41.750
Regarding the Beifu Reform,

00:42.240 --> 00:43.570
what do you intend to do?

00:44.920 --> 00:45.790
Your Majesty,

00:46.110 --> 00:48.240
my reform will proceed in three steps.

00:49.670 --> 00:51.790
Firstly, eliminate long-standing flaws,

00:51.790 --> 00:53.150
restructure the military system,

00:53.150 --> 00:54.520
appoint talents of humble origins,

00:54.520 --> 00:56.320
and employ generals by ability alone.

00:56.320 --> 00:58.600
Secondly,
forge stronger armor and weapons,

00:58.600 --> 01:00.030
and expand
the transportation of provisions

01:00.030 --> 01:01.520
to ensure steady military supplies.

01:01.520 --> 01:02.030
Thirdly...

01:02.030 --> 01:04.400
What is Prince Qi's take on this plan?

01:05.280 --> 01:07.760
Prince Qi and I share a bond like brothers

01:08.280 --> 01:09.430
as well as deep trust.

01:09.430 --> 01:10.310
I believe that

01:11.400 --> 01:14.150
as long as His Highness
and I join hands...

01:23.280 --> 01:24.590
Even today,

01:25.590 --> 01:26.950
you still think

01:27.510 --> 01:30.510
that you and Prince Qi
share a bond like brothers

01:31.230 --> 01:32.470
as well as deep trust?

01:36.950 --> 01:37.870
Now,

01:39.710 --> 01:40.950
do you understand

01:41.920 --> 01:45.840
why I insisted on keeping Xie Jiayu

01:46.920 --> 01:48.400
by your side?

02:00.870 --> 02:02.040
I understand now.

02:04.680 --> 02:06.340
The way of checks and balances

02:07.230 --> 02:08.630
is the emperor's art.

02:09.470 --> 02:10.400
Therefore,

02:11.150 --> 02:12.470
Xie Jiayu

02:13.120 --> 02:13.870
is my way

02:14.750 --> 02:17.870
of keeping a balance
between you and Prince Qi.

03:49.390 --> 03:53.220
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:53.360 --> 03:56.190
[Episode 15]

03:56.270 --> 04:00.150
[Lingfeng Fort]

04:02.260 --> 04:04.950
[Cui Jun, Master of the Cui family]

04:05.430 --> 04:08.280
Father, why are you so fond of pine trees?

04:08.560 --> 04:09.680
They can endure cold and drought.

04:09.680 --> 04:11.150
Scatter a handful of seeds anywhere,

04:11.150 --> 04:12.210
and they will grow.

04:12.520 --> 04:13.840
But Mother told me that

04:14.310 --> 04:16.260
you loved loquat flowers the most
when you were young.

04:16.260 --> 04:18.860
Even Mother loved
making loquat wine the most.

04:20.640 --> 04:21.959
People change.

04:22.750 --> 04:24.950
I will set off for Jiankang in a few days.

04:25.070 --> 04:26.270
I'm afraid that, by this time

04:26.270 --> 04:27.720
next year,
I won't be able to accompany you

04:27.720 --> 04:29.160
to pay respects to Mother together.

04:29.160 --> 04:29.870
Today,

04:31.040 --> 04:32.560
let me pour wine for you

04:32.560 --> 04:33.820
one last time, Father.

04:46.040 --> 04:47.750
You have arranged such a grand marriage

04:47.750 --> 04:48.950
for me, Father,

04:50.720 --> 04:52.720
but I only feel restless and uneasy.

04:52.950 --> 04:55.610
The Cui family is hailed
as the top noble family.

04:56.630 --> 04:58.360
But what have you done, Father?

04:59.360 --> 05:01.360
Do you really think no one knows?

05:01.870 --> 05:03.690
You've privately run illegal mines

05:03.690 --> 05:04.560
and tricked women

05:04.560 --> 05:06.310
into dying in the mines unjustly.

05:06.310 --> 05:07.830
Your actions are

05:07.830 --> 05:10.160
enough to ruin our Cui family completely.

05:10.830 --> 05:11.480
Shao'an!

05:11.480 --> 05:12.680
You don't need to call him.

05:12.680 --> 05:14.920
I have already led Shao'an
out of Lingfeng Fort.

05:14.920 --> 05:16.950
And I also told Xie Jiayu the hiding place

05:16.950 --> 05:18.810
of her mother, Princess Yunzhao.

05:18.830 --> 05:20.920
By now, they must have left Lingfeng Fort.

05:20.920 --> 05:23.980
Everything about Lingfeng Fort is
about to be exposed.

05:25.160 --> 05:25.920
Guards!

05:26.680 --> 05:28.920
If you plead guilty
together with me today,

05:28.920 --> 05:31.780
our Cui family might still
have a chance to survive.

05:40.560 --> 05:42.690
Lady Jiayu, my young lady ordered that

05:42.920 --> 05:44.190
after we get Her Highness out,

05:44.190 --> 05:46.590
you must leave Lingfeng Fort immediately.

05:54.390 --> 05:56.120
Do you really think I'm stupid?

05:56.159 --> 05:57.750
I knew Lingyi was a traitor

05:57.750 --> 05:59.920
and wanted to help you save the Princess.

05:59.920 --> 06:00.980
Where is Xiao Wuyi?

06:03.240 --> 06:04.360
Behind you.

06:09.390 --> 06:11.560
Xiao Wuyi, how did you know
there was a trap?

06:11.560 --> 06:13.360
Were we also tricked by Young Lady Cui?

06:13.360 --> 06:14.890
Cui Lingyi didn't trick us.

06:15.010 --> 06:17.290
Instead, she was also deceived by them.

06:18.680 --> 06:19.920
Last night,
Cui Lingyi spread the fake news

06:19.920 --> 06:21.920
that we had fled from Lingfeng Fort.

06:22.070 --> 06:22.750
And you

06:22.950 --> 06:25.680
searched for us with great fanfare
in the middle of the night.

06:25.680 --> 06:26.920
Wasn't it to deliberately tell us that

06:26.920 --> 06:28.120
you had left the city?

06:28.270 --> 06:29.480
If my guess is right,

06:29.720 --> 06:30.680
you lurked in the dark

06:30.680 --> 06:32.280
soon after you left the city.

06:40.800 --> 06:41.920
We encountered no obstacles at all

06:41.920 --> 06:43.190
on our way to the back mountain.

06:43.190 --> 06:45.360
Including that maid
who suddenly appeared just now,

06:45.360 --> 06:46.890
everything is suspicious.

06:47.310 --> 06:49.970
Someone must have
lured us here intentionally.

06:52.950 --> 06:55.430
You think you can bring me down this way?

06:55.720 --> 06:56.270
You think

06:56.270 --> 06:58.600
you can save
our Cui family just like this?

06:58.800 --> 07:01.310
You think I would drink the poisoned wine?

07:05.550 --> 07:07.870
I am the Master of Lingfeng Fort.

07:08.560 --> 07:10.630
And you will soon
enter the Eastern Palace and marry

07:10.630 --> 07:12.030
Prince Qi to become his consort.

07:12.030 --> 07:13.830
In the future, you will be the first lady

07:13.830 --> 07:14.960
like Empress Wenxi.

07:15.270 --> 07:17.480
Our Cui family has laid low
for over 20 years

07:17.480 --> 07:18.630
just for today

07:18.630 --> 07:20.720
to revive our family.

07:21.040 --> 07:24.000
But you insisted on ruining
the glory of our Cui family

07:24.000 --> 07:26.000
at this very moment

07:26.190 --> 07:28.870
and destroying my 20 years
of great efforts.

07:32.430 --> 07:33.480
I suppose your sister

07:33.480 --> 07:35.070
has already been captured by now.

07:35.070 --> 07:36.400
Hand over the Princess,

07:37.360 --> 07:39.390
or I'll kill you right now.

07:39.520 --> 07:40.920
Ouch! It hurts...

07:46.430 --> 07:46.950
Mother!

07:49.830 --> 07:51.120
What an impressive scheme.

07:51.120 --> 07:52.159
Young Lord Xiao,

07:53.120 --> 07:54.190
I've heard a lot about you.

07:54.190 --> 07:55.250
Put the sword down.

08:02.040 --> 08:02.870
Father.

08:10.000 --> 08:10.560
Father,

08:11.000 --> 08:11.830
Lingyi is already engaged

08:11.830 --> 08:13.120
and will get married soon.

08:13.120 --> 08:13.950
Xiao Wuyi and the Princess

08:13.950 --> 08:15.120
are both in our hands now.

08:15.120 --> 08:16.650
There won't be any problem.

08:17.070 --> 08:18.730
Please let Lingyi go, Father.

08:20.310 --> 08:20.950
Father,

08:21.310 --> 08:22.840
are you still going to use me

08:23.560 --> 08:25.090
to force Shao'an to do evil?

08:26.040 --> 08:26.720
Lingyi...

08:27.240 --> 08:29.360
Are you still going to use Shao'an
to force me

08:29.360 --> 08:31.360
to cover up the truth for the family?

08:32.080 --> 08:33.200
Since we were young,

08:33.200 --> 08:35.840
you've kept instigating conflicts
between Shao'an and me.

08:35.840 --> 08:37.240
Whenever you praised me,

08:38.630 --> 08:39.600
you'd scold Shao'an

08:39.600 --> 08:40.909
as if he was worthless.

08:41.080 --> 08:42.120
I didn't understand back then.

08:42.120 --> 08:43.780
I was only at odds with Shao'an

08:44.000 --> 08:45.910
in order to please you.

08:47.090 --> 08:48.890
What you want is never children,

08:49.360 --> 08:50.030
but merely

08:50.030 --> 08:51.690
two pawns under your control!

08:52.030 --> 08:55.030
I'd rather die
than be manipulated by you again!

08:56.790 --> 08:58.240
Do you think Princess Yunzhao

08:58.240 --> 08:59.510
is some sort of good person?

08:59.510 --> 09:00.440
Do you think she stayed

09:00.440 --> 09:02.180
in order to expose the Cui family?

09:02.180 --> 09:03.750
Do you think she lured Xiao Wuyi

09:03.750 --> 09:05.200
over here to help you reveal

09:05.200 --> 09:06.930
the dark side of the Cui family?

09:07.150 --> 09:10.350
Everything she did was
for the Phoenix Heart Token I hold!

09:11.750 --> 09:13.270
Whatever her purpose,

09:13.440 --> 09:14.440
all I want is for her to destroy

09:14.440 --> 09:15.870
everything here!

09:16.070 --> 09:16.630
Lingyi,

09:16.980 --> 09:18.610
how could you talk to Father like that?

09:18.610 --> 09:19.960
Kneel and apologize to him!

09:19.960 --> 09:20.670
Shao'an,

09:20.960 --> 09:22.720
the real lunatic in our family

09:23.320 --> 09:24.840
is our father!

09:33.360 --> 09:34.000
Lingyi...

09:34.870 --> 09:35.910
Lingyi!

09:36.200 --> 09:36.960
Lingyi...

09:38.440 --> 09:39.320
Lingyi...

09:47.750 --> 09:48.810
Princess Yunzhao,

09:49.080 --> 09:50.360
your daughter and your reinforcement

09:50.360 --> 09:51.720
are both in my hands.

09:52.080 --> 09:55.210
Do you still refuse to hand over
the Phoenix Heart Token?

10:04.360 --> 10:05.080
Mother.

10:07.270 --> 10:08.200
Are you alright?

10:11.670 --> 10:13.480
Cui Jun, how dare you

10:13.670 --> 10:14.960
tamper with my letter?

10:15.870 --> 10:18.470
I did use the family letter
to inform Xiao Wuyi,

10:18.600 --> 10:20.600
but I did something with the letter.

10:20.720 --> 10:22.270
It should never have reached Jiayu.

10:22.270 --> 10:23.730
You deliberately set it up

10:24.600 --> 10:25.740
to lure Jiayu over here.

10:25.740 --> 10:26.550
Yes, I did it.

10:29.030 --> 10:30.160
I also needed to know

10:30.270 --> 10:32.790
who you plotted to get
the Phoenix Heart Token

10:32.790 --> 10:34.190
and the mines for, right?

10:35.530 --> 10:36.290
Mother,

10:37.030 --> 10:38.030
what does he mean?

10:38.100 --> 10:40.550
Your Highness,
you're indeed a good mother.

10:40.550 --> 10:42.720
Everything you did was for your daughter.

10:42.720 --> 10:44.630
System reform, northern expedition—

10:44.630 --> 10:47.270
actually, the one
who really needs the minerals

10:47.270 --> 10:48.440
is Young Lord Xiao.

10:49.130 --> 10:51.050
But your daughter is in his hands.

10:52.360 --> 10:55.510
As her mother,
of course you have to yield.

10:56.720 --> 10:59.750
Therefore, you came to Guazhou
for Young Lord Xiao

11:00.600 --> 11:02.400
to find the Phoenix Heart Token.

11:02.950 --> 11:03.950
So you really have

11:05.390 --> 11:06.790
the Phoenix Heart Token.

11:07.120 --> 11:08.150
You found this mine

11:08.150 --> 11:10.750
under the guidance
of the Phoenix Heart Token.

11:11.600 --> 11:13.360
I have indeed decoded it.

11:14.270 --> 11:16.720
So there's no way I can let you go.

11:16.840 --> 11:17.630
Cui Jun,

11:18.600 --> 11:21.130
even if you kill and silence us all,
the secret

11:22.030 --> 11:24.870
of the Cuis and the Phoenix Heart Token
still can't remain hidden.

11:24.870 --> 11:25.800
Young Lord Xiao,

11:25.870 --> 11:27.530
instead of worrying about me,

11:27.840 --> 11:28.600
right now,

11:29.120 --> 11:31.150
you'd better worry about yourself.

11:31.750 --> 11:33.870
The secret guards you planted
have been exposed.

11:33.870 --> 11:35.870
No one will come to save you anymore.

11:35.870 --> 11:38.390
Princess, I'll only give you 2 days.

11:38.750 --> 11:40.910
If you still refuse
to hand over the Phoenix Heart Token,

11:40.910 --> 11:43.440
your daughter will die for sure.

11:50.160 --> 11:53.500
[Court of Judicial Review]

11:58.790 --> 12:00.320
Look what I got for you.

12:02.120 --> 12:03.390
I didn't expect that, after so many years,

12:02.340 --> 12:05.790
[Yang Zhang, Guazhou County Sheriff]

12:04.290 --> 12:05.690
you still remember that I

12:06.080 --> 12:08.740
love the longans
from Nanzhou the most, Master.

12:15.600 --> 12:16.670
This time,

12:17.200 --> 12:18.510
you did a great job.

12:19.120 --> 12:21.960
You sent
Cui Jun's contaminated military provisions

12:21.960 --> 12:23.150
to the Northern Border,

12:23.150 --> 12:25.950
leading to an outbreak of plague
in the Beifu Army.

12:25.960 --> 12:27.200
It also caused the noble families

12:27.200 --> 12:29.730
to impeach the Beifu Reform
one after another

12:30.150 --> 12:32.000
and quietly

12:32.030 --> 12:34.120
lured Xiao Wuyi to Cui Jun's place.

12:35.120 --> 12:36.910
It's been over 2 decades.

12:37.150 --> 12:40.600
This grudge should finally come to an end.

12:40.670 --> 12:41.360
Master,

12:41.360 --> 12:44.390
I heard that the unjust case
of the An and Lu families back then

12:44.390 --> 12:47.000
was all traced back
to Empress Wenxi of the Cui family.

12:47.000 --> 12:48.000
Is it true?

12:48.640 --> 12:50.240
If Xiao Wuyi can bring down

12:50.270 --> 12:52.000
the Cuis, Empress Wenxi's maternal family,

12:52.000 --> 12:53.270
this time,

12:53.270 --> 12:55.750
the secret of the An and Lu families
from back then

12:55.750 --> 12:57.750
might finally come to light.

12:58.120 --> 12:59.320
If so,

12:59.910 --> 13:01.360
you will be

13:03.270 --> 13:05.390
my greatest benefactor

13:06.270 --> 13:07.840
for the rest of my life.

13:10.240 --> 13:11.870
Your grace of teaching
gave me a second life,

13:11.870 --> 13:13.320
equal to my parents' care and love.

13:13.320 --> 13:14.510
Now that I got a chance to do you a favor,

13:14.510 --> 13:15.960
even if I die for it,

13:16.230 --> 13:17.440
I still can't repay you enough.

13:17.440 --> 13:20.270
It is already
the greatest fortune of my life!

13:24.050 --> 13:27.580
[Imperial Academy]

13:26.080 --> 13:28.670
Master, we just got the news
from the Court of Judicial Review.

13:28.260 --> 13:31.540
[Bingzhu, butler of Xie Mansion]

13:29.200 --> 13:30.630
Yang Zhang, Guazhou County Sheriff,

13:30.630 --> 13:32.890
committed suicide in prison out of fear.

13:39.840 --> 13:41.150
The body can't be kept.

13:41.270 --> 13:44.070
Send his body to Puzhao Temple tonight
and burn it.

13:44.380 --> 13:45.110
Understood.

13:48.840 --> 13:49.790
Anything else?

13:50.320 --> 13:52.870
The subordinates Young Lord Xiao
planted outside Lingfeng Fort

13:52.870 --> 13:54.140
have all been wiped out.

13:54.140 --> 13:55.870
Cui Jun has captured Young Lord Xiao.

13:55.870 --> 13:57.470
How could Xiao Wuyi have made

13:57.910 --> 13:59.510
such hasty preparations?

13:59.720 --> 14:00.720
Our informant reported

14:00.720 --> 14:02.000
that Young Lord Xiao entered

14:02.000 --> 14:04.200
Lingfeng Fort early for our young lady.

14:04.750 --> 14:05.840
Xie Jiayu?

14:06.630 --> 14:08.110
How come she's in Guazhou?

14:08.550 --> 14:09.500
Not only the Young Lady,

14:09.500 --> 14:11.230
but the Princess is also there.

14:11.390 --> 14:14.080
Her Highness wrote to the Young Lady
and made her go to Guazhou.

14:14.080 --> 14:16.230
Cui Jun has seized them all now,

14:16.720 --> 14:20.630
using the Young Lady to force Her Highness
to hand over the Phoenix Heart Token.

14:20.630 --> 14:22.030
The Phoenix Heart Token?

14:22.550 --> 14:25.910
I see.
Cui Jun is Empress Wenxi's older brother.

14:26.510 --> 14:28.600
If Yunzhao has the Phoenix Heart Token

14:28.600 --> 14:31.480
and wants to unite her old subordinates
against Prince Qi,

14:31.480 --> 14:33.630
Cui Jun is the best ally.

14:41.870 --> 14:42.840
Xiao Wuyi,

14:44.240 --> 14:45.840
was Cui Jun telling the truth

14:46.270 --> 14:47.270
just now?

14:48.080 --> 14:49.280
Did my mother look for

14:49.790 --> 14:51.650
the Phoenix Heart Tokens for you?

14:51.870 --> 14:52.510
Yes.

14:54.910 --> 14:55.790
You could say that.

14:55.790 --> 14:58.190
My mother never meddles in court politics.

14:58.270 --> 14:59.720
If someone hadn't forced her,

14:59.720 --> 15:02.510
she wouldn't have
taken the initiative to get involved.

15:02.510 --> 15:03.750
Did you use me to threaten her?

15:03.750 --> 15:04.440
No,

15:06.040 --> 15:08.040
I've never used you to threaten her.

15:09.200 --> 15:11.000
But this matter is complicated.

15:12.080 --> 15:13.440
I'll explain it to you later.

15:13.440 --> 15:14.510
But my mother agreed to help you

15:14.510 --> 15:15.360
because of me.

15:21.680 --> 15:24.810
I once thought that
after my mother and father divorced,

15:24.910 --> 15:27.440
she would finally be able
to live for herself,

15:28.400 --> 15:30.640
travel to places she had never seen,

15:31.200 --> 15:33.560
and lead a carefree life
she had never had.

15:34.720 --> 15:35.850
I didn't expect that

15:36.910 --> 15:39.000
she'd still be dragged
into this because of me,

15:39.000 --> 15:40.130
utilized by others,

15:40.550 --> 15:42.550
and end up in such a desperate state.

15:42.870 --> 15:43.930
I once thought that

15:45.870 --> 15:48.470
you cared about me
in Prince Jing'an's Mansion

15:48.630 --> 15:50.630
and allowed me to come and go freely,

15:51.840 --> 15:54.040
all because you were just a good person.

15:56.510 --> 15:57.670
I was too stupid.

15:58.000 --> 15:59.120
Everything I did

16:00.440 --> 16:01.480
was never about

16:01.480 --> 16:03.280
making a deal with the Princess.

16:04.120 --> 16:04.960
Xie Jiayu,

16:06.270 --> 16:07.630
did you really not

16:10.150 --> 16:11.480
feel anything at all?

16:12.760 --> 16:14.120
Am I wrong, Xiao Wuyi?

16:14.910 --> 16:17.150
You've been using me
from the very beginning.

16:17.150 --> 16:18.960
At first, when you didn't even know
who I was,

16:18.960 --> 16:21.320
you used me to quell
Prince Changsha's rebellion.

16:21.320 --> 16:22.580
When you knew who I was,

16:22.670 --> 16:23.960
you used my freedom

16:23.960 --> 16:24.630
and my life

16:24.630 --> 16:26.750
to force my mother to hand over
the Phoenix Heart Token,

16:26.750 --> 16:28.320
putting her in danger!

16:38.150 --> 16:38.790
Yes.

16:45.630 --> 16:46.630
It's all my fault.

16:57.510 --> 16:58.570
What is this sound?

16:59.390 --> 17:00.720
Not the sound of a human.

17:03.880 --> 17:06.609
There is an underground river
beneath this mine,

17:07.270 --> 17:08.550
where the water is not clean.

17:08.550 --> 17:09.829
Taken or applied,

17:10.550 --> 17:12.310
it drives people mad

17:12.880 --> 17:13.930
and turns them into beasts,

17:13.930 --> 17:15.280
just like him.

17:21.510 --> 17:24.400
Do you know how many people
my father had killed

17:24.579 --> 17:26.250
until he got such a monster?

17:38.550 --> 17:39.590
No more struggling.

17:39.590 --> 17:41.320
This candle is specially made.

17:41.680 --> 17:43.350
You can't use your martial arts anymore.

17:43.350 --> 17:44.960
Hand over the Phoenix Heart Token.

17:44.960 --> 17:45.720
Otherwise,

17:46.200 --> 17:48.060
I don't mind letting this monster

17:48.380 --> 17:49.540
deal with Xie Jiayu.

17:55.270 --> 17:55.920
Very well.

17:59.400 --> 18:00.350
Release him.

18:08.000 --> 18:08.640
Jiayu!

18:21.110 --> 18:21.720
Xiao Wuyi!

18:26.440 --> 18:28.300
-Stay here and watch.
-Xiao Wuyi!

18:30.270 --> 18:31.920
He has little inner energy now.

18:31.920 --> 18:33.270
How about we give him 15 minutes?

18:33.270 --> 18:34.870
It won't take him 15 minutes.

18:46.920 --> 18:48.250
You trust him that much?

18:49.920 --> 18:51.070
He will win for sure.

18:58.970 --> 18:59.770
Xiao Wuyi...

19:12.000 --> 19:12.720
Xiao Wuyi.

19:45.960 --> 19:47.590
Grand Tutor, you must've come

19:47.590 --> 19:50.160
late at night for something important.

19:56.450 --> 19:57.850
What on earth happened?

19:57.880 --> 20:00.240
Have you heard
of the Phoenix Heart Tokens?

20:00.240 --> 20:02.310
When the Phoenix Heart Tokens appear,
peace shall be restored in the world.

20:02.310 --> 20:04.550
Who in Ye hasn't heard about it?

20:05.400 --> 20:07.120
It is the hope of the people.

20:07.200 --> 20:09.960
What if Empress Wenxi really
had the Phoenix Heart Tokens

20:09.960 --> 20:11.160
and passed them down?

20:11.680 --> 20:13.720
Since Yunzhao was her closest friend,

20:13.720 --> 20:15.510
and Cui Jun was her older brother,

20:15.510 --> 20:17.030
the two of them are the most likely

20:17.030 --> 20:19.960
to be entrusted by Empress Wenxi.

20:23.270 --> 20:25.800
Even if the Phoenix Heart Tokens
truly exist,

20:27.240 --> 20:28.440
the Northern Qin people back then

20:28.440 --> 20:30.570
already wiped out Crown Prince Wenxi.

20:30.720 --> 20:32.590
Those people only have
the Phoenix Heart Tokens

20:32.590 --> 20:34.120
but not Crown Prince Wenxi.

20:34.550 --> 20:36.750
They pose no threat to my brother at all.

20:40.550 --> 20:41.410
Your Highness,

20:42.400 --> 20:43.640
what if I told you

20:44.310 --> 20:45.310
your brother

20:45.980 --> 20:48.390
is not of the Ye bloodline at all?

20:51.790 --> 20:53.520
Watch your words, Grand Tutor.

20:57.750 --> 21:00.480
Yunzhao has long suspected
Prince Qi's origins.

21:00.750 --> 21:02.350
She went to Guazhou this time

21:02.550 --> 21:03.590
probably just to use

21:03.590 --> 21:05.400
the Phoenix Heart Token in her hands

21:05.400 --> 21:07.330
to command the other Token holders

21:07.750 --> 21:10.440
and support
the Imperial Li family of Ye again.

21:14.750 --> 21:15.950
How is that possible?

21:16.680 --> 21:17.480
How could my brother not be...

21:17.480 --> 21:18.720
Your trip to Guazhou this time

21:18.720 --> 21:20.160
is nominally to escort the bride,

21:20.160 --> 21:21.550
but the real purpose is to cooperate

21:21.550 --> 21:23.810
with Young Lord Xiao to capture the Cuis.

21:24.240 --> 21:26.350
Remember, besides purging the Cuis,

21:26.350 --> 21:28.070
you absolutely cannot
let the Phoenix Heart Token

21:28.070 --> 21:29.830
fall into Xiao Wuyi's hands.

21:30.440 --> 21:31.400
You must not

21:31.960 --> 21:35.110
let Yunzhao ruin Prince Qi's future.

21:44.240 --> 21:46.240
Brother, the clothes are fixed.

21:46.480 --> 21:48.080
Try them on when you're free.

21:50.240 --> 21:50.920
Lejun.

21:53.830 --> 21:54.590
Put this on.

22:00.070 --> 22:01.200
This sachet

22:02.200 --> 22:03.350
was sewn for you

22:03.920 --> 22:05.480
by Mother back then.

22:07.110 --> 22:09.000
I heard that a strange disease is raging
in Guazhou.

22:09.000 --> 22:10.030
It has Bishou lotuses inside,

22:10.030 --> 22:11.310
with detoxifying effects.

22:11.310 --> 22:12.720
Since this was made by Mother,

22:12.720 --> 22:15.380
it can definitely keep you safe
on your journey.

22:16.640 --> 22:18.100
Brother, you are so silly.

22:18.720 --> 22:20.110
It's been so many years.

22:20.550 --> 22:22.480
The effects must've long worn off.

22:31.310 --> 22:32.970
You will always be my brother.

22:33.400 --> 22:34.720
The brother I know

22:35.270 --> 22:36.550
is Li Mao, who has always

22:36.550 --> 22:38.480
stuck with me through everything.

22:38.550 --> 22:39.220
What?

22:42.590 --> 22:43.850
Don't worry, Brother.

22:44.120 --> 22:47.030
I will not fail your trust
on this journey.

22:47.880 --> 22:49.940
I will bring the Cui family to justice

22:51.350 --> 22:52.810
and return safe and sound.

23:33.830 --> 23:34.830
You irritated me

23:35.680 --> 23:36.750
on purpose just now

23:37.920 --> 23:40.000
because you wanted me
to help you kill him, right?

23:40.000 --> 23:42.530
I've been sick
of that bastard for a long time.

23:42.930 --> 23:44.590
You hated what your father has done,

23:44.590 --> 23:46.070
but you didn't dare to resist.

23:46.070 --> 23:48.600
So you could only
use Xiao Wuyi and me as pawns.

23:49.350 --> 23:50.880
My father would do anything

23:50.950 --> 23:52.590
for the Phoenix Heart Tokens.

23:52.590 --> 23:53.510
I needed to see

23:53.510 --> 23:55.640
your determination and capabilities

23:55.830 --> 23:57.160
to go against my father.

23:57.350 --> 23:58.000
Xiao Wuyi,

23:58.920 --> 24:00.380
when will your men arrive?

24:03.310 --> 24:04.830
It's fine if you don't want to tell me,

24:04.830 --> 24:06.830
as long as there are reinforcements.

24:06.830 --> 24:08.860
The area outside the cave is
heavily guarded by my father's men.

24:08.860 --> 24:10.310
You'd better not act rashly

24:10.310 --> 24:11.920
before the reinforcements arrive.

24:11.920 --> 24:14.070
I'll remove all the candles outside.

24:15.270 --> 24:17.330
This is the only thing I can do for you.

24:17.790 --> 24:18.440
Hold on.

24:25.550 --> 24:27.590
This is what your sister asked me to give

24:27.590 --> 24:28.920
to you when she was alive.

24:28.920 --> 24:30.520
If this plan fails tomorrow,

24:31.830 --> 24:33.490
I will definitely end up dead.

24:34.270 --> 24:36.590
Please pass this letter on to my brother.

24:47.440 --> 24:49.100
If you are going to make a move,

24:49.720 --> 24:52.050
you'd better rescue all the people below.

24:59.680 --> 25:01.880
When will your reinforcements arrive?

25:03.640 --> 25:05.640
Qing Long and Yan Yue will send word.

25:07.270 --> 25:08.240
Don't worry,

25:08.790 --> 25:10.350
they will definitely ensure the safety

25:10.350 --> 25:12.550
of the Princess and Yuan Xiaoliu first.

25:14.350 --> 25:15.350
Then let's rest

25:15.530 --> 25:16.990
to conserve our strength.

25:34.700 --> 25:37.430
♪ One glance from near stirs my heart ♪

25:37.650 --> 25:40.200
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

25:41.900 --> 25:45.910
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

25:46.080 --> 25:48.080
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

25:50.040 --> 25:53.040
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

25:53.450 --> 25:57.820
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

25:58.410 --> 26:01.320
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

26:02.250 --> 26:05.070
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

26:02.680 --> 26:03.810
Don't overthink it.

26:04.070 --> 26:05.680
I'm just afraid
your injuries are too severe

26:05.680 --> 26:06.880
for you to make it out of here alive.

26:06.590 --> 26:10.930
♪ You know me and decided to
live and die together ♪

26:10.950 --> 26:14.610
♪ Believe in my persistence that
I won't run away ♪

26:14.630 --> 26:18.770
♪ You know I'm unyielding ♪

26:19.400 --> 26:22.320
♪ Don't give up or dodge ♪

26:23.220 --> 26:26.970
♪ Sincere hearts remain as of old ♪

26:43.550 --> 26:44.270
I...

26:45.640 --> 26:48.370
♪ One glance from near stirs my heart ♪

26:46.880 --> 26:48.830
I'm not treating you well
because of the Phoenix Heart Token

26:48.590 --> 26:51.140
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

26:49.720 --> 26:51.180
that the Princess gave me.

26:51.960 --> 26:53.070
Both Her Highness and I

26:52.840 --> 26:56.850
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

26:54.680 --> 26:56.880
wish for you to live freely and happily.

26:56.910 --> 26:58.910
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

27:00.980 --> 27:03.980
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

27:04.160 --> 27:04.960
Jiayu.

27:04.390 --> 27:08.760
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

27:08.720 --> 27:09.310
I...

27:09.350 --> 27:12.260
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

27:09.640 --> 27:10.310
Xiao Wuyi.

27:12.200 --> 27:13.000
Are you sure

27:13.190 --> 27:16.010
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

27:13.240 --> 27:15.040
you can rescue all those people?

27:15.790 --> 27:16.590
I can.

27:17.630 --> 27:21.400
♪ You know me, seeing things
through from start to finish ♪

27:17.880 --> 27:19.070
You're bragging.

27:20.970 --> 27:22.200
I can pull it off if you trust me.

27:21.920 --> 27:26.030
♪ You see my move
under rebellious cover ♪

27:26.300 --> 27:30.280
♪ You know me, I'm willing to be
with you till the end ♪

27:28.310 --> 27:29.030
Okay.

27:30.310 --> 27:34.240
♪ Burn the fire in my heart ♪

27:30.790 --> 27:31.680
I believe you.

27:36.520 --> 27:39.090
♪ Sincere hearts remain as of old ♪

27:46.070 --> 27:48.870
I know this risky path I walk
may lead only to death.

27:49.310 --> 27:52.880
However, the Cui family's evil deeds
actually started because of me.

27:52.880 --> 27:55.030
If I hadn't tried to outdo you

27:55.640 --> 27:57.720
and reminded Father
that, compared to adult men,

27:57.720 --> 27:59.310
perhaps women might be better suited

27:59.310 --> 28:00.920
to the narrow mine tunnels

28:01.120 --> 28:03.400
and wouldn't be discovered
by the authorities,

28:03.400 --> 28:06.070
we wouldn't have committed
so many murders now.

28:07.110 --> 28:09.680
Plenty of women were tricked
into coming to Lingfeng Fort

28:09.680 --> 28:12.340
and lost their lives
for a bit of grain and money.

28:12.830 --> 28:15.640
Thankfully, Princess Yunzhao discovered
the secret of the mines.

28:15.640 --> 28:16.350
I saved her

28:16.640 --> 28:18.200
and helped her lure Young Lord Xiao here

28:18.200 --> 28:19.800
in order to atone for my sins.

28:20.270 --> 28:23.480
Shao'an, I know you want me
to leave Lingfeng Fort

28:23.750 --> 28:25.140
and live a peaceful life.

28:25.140 --> 28:28.030
But since the mistake has been made,
I must pay with my life.

28:28.030 --> 28:29.880
If you continue to help the evildoer,

28:29.880 --> 28:31.740
I will not be able to rest in peace.

28:31.880 --> 28:34.280
I hope my death
can ignite your will to live.

28:34.590 --> 28:37.350
Only you know the way to save those women.

28:39.390 --> 28:42.180
[Lingfeng Fort]

28:47.480 --> 28:48.400
Hey!

28:48.920 --> 28:50.880
Who the heck locked me up?

28:51.270 --> 28:52.200
Say something!

28:53.160 --> 28:54.000
It's been so many days,

28:54.000 --> 28:55.350
and no one's ever come!

28:55.480 --> 28:56.740
Why not kill him, Master?

28:56.740 --> 28:57.410
What if...

29:00.790 --> 29:01.920
Prince Qi's escort team

29:01.920 --> 29:03.320
is already near Guazhou.

29:03.480 --> 29:04.070
Princess Pingning

29:04.070 --> 29:05.590
came in person this time.

29:06.030 --> 29:07.360
They came right on time.

29:09.150 --> 29:11.200
How many days has it been
since we last heard from Cui Xi?

29:11.200 --> 29:13.000
There are new updates every day.

29:13.160 --> 29:15.070
Everything is as usual
at the Cui Mansion in Jiankang.

29:15.070 --> 29:15.830
I see.

29:18.510 --> 29:19.110
By the way,

29:20.200 --> 29:21.660
you must not mistreat him.

29:22.160 --> 29:22.890
Understood.

29:26.750 --> 29:28.720
Are you kidnapping me
for my money or my looks?

29:28.720 --> 29:29.980
Just tell me directly!

29:30.550 --> 29:31.750
I'm fine with either!

29:39.000 --> 29:40.130
Greetings, Father.

29:40.160 --> 29:41.720
Prince Qi has sent his younger sister,

29:41.720 --> 29:42.850
Princess Pingning,

29:43.070 --> 29:44.750
to Lingfeng Fortress
to escort the bride.

29:44.750 --> 29:45.750
From now on,

29:46.720 --> 29:48.380
she will be your older sister,

29:48.920 --> 29:49.920
Cui Lingyi.

30:02.160 --> 30:02.710
Father.

30:03.920 --> 30:04.990
She is not my...

30:08.640 --> 30:09.900
Turn your head around.

30:14.750 --> 30:15.590
Bow.

30:23.180 --> 30:24.340
S-Sister.

30:32.430 --> 30:33.680
Xie Jiayu

30:34.030 --> 30:36.830
made the white silk flower
for your sister, right?

30:38.920 --> 30:40.960
Didn't you miss your sister so much?

30:41.150 --> 30:43.150
Then stay here and behave yourself.

30:43.640 --> 30:44.750
Without my order,

30:45.790 --> 30:48.650
you shall not leave this place
even by a single step.

30:59.400 --> 31:02.380
[Lingfeng Fort]

31:05.350 --> 31:07.000
I spent over 20 years

31:07.920 --> 31:10.520
cracking the secret
in the Phoenix Heart Token

31:11.240 --> 31:14.100
and discovering the iron mine
under this mountain.

31:15.070 --> 31:16.200
But it's a pity that

31:17.240 --> 31:20.200
an accident happened
halfway through the excavation.

31:20.200 --> 31:21.830
The groundwater has been contaminated,

31:21.830 --> 31:24.350
and anyone who touches it
will get hit by a strange disease.

31:24.350 --> 31:25.550
Last night, Xiao Wuyi

31:25.680 --> 31:28.010
killed a maniac with the strange disease.

31:28.440 --> 31:31.270
Your Highness, if you still refuse
to hand over the Phoenix Heart Token,

31:31.270 --> 31:33.070
then the next one to get infected

31:33.400 --> 31:34.720
will be Xie Jiayu.

31:38.030 --> 31:39.230
If she gets infected,

31:40.030 --> 31:41.640
I wonder if Young Lord Xiao

31:42.440 --> 31:44.400
would give her a quick death.

31:49.440 --> 31:50.640
Take this hairpin

31:51.480 --> 31:54.080
and go to the Nandu Wharf
we agreed on back then.

31:55.000 --> 31:56.240
Seeing this hairpin,

31:56.720 --> 31:58.180
someone will contact you.

32:08.750 --> 32:10.110
I can't believe you hid
the Phoenix Heart Token

32:10.110 --> 32:12.000
at the old Nandu Wharf.

32:12.720 --> 32:13.400
Guards,

32:14.030 --> 32:16.640
seal off all the mines
at the foot of the mountain

32:16.640 --> 32:18.750
and let no one get out of there.

32:18.830 --> 32:19.400
-Understood.
-Understood.

32:19.400 --> 32:20.660
Take Her Highness away

32:20.810 --> 32:21.670
and lock her up.

32:22.200 --> 32:22.830
Cui Jun!

32:23.350 --> 32:24.480
You broke your word!

32:24.550 --> 32:25.790
It's not the first time.

32:25.790 --> 32:28.640
Aren't you afraid
that everything I told you is fake?

32:28.640 --> 32:31.510
The worst case is that I'll kill both you

32:32.000 --> 32:33.060
and your daughter.

32:33.310 --> 32:34.110
Take her away.

32:41.960 --> 32:44.220
Stop wandering. You're making me dizzy.

32:45.310 --> 32:47.790
Do you think Qing Long and Yan Yue
have been caught?

32:47.790 --> 32:48.960
Where are your reinforcements?

32:48.960 --> 32:50.000
Why hasn't there been any response?

32:50.000 --> 32:51.030
Rest assured.

32:51.680 --> 32:53.200
Before I entered Lingfeng Fort,

32:53.200 --> 32:55.800
the reinforcements were already
on their way.

32:56.920 --> 32:58.590
I didn't come here because of

32:58.590 --> 33:00.320
the Princess's family letter.

33:00.680 --> 33:01.790
Before I came here,

33:02.200 --> 33:03.790
some people in the Beifu Army

33:03.790 --> 33:06.070
contracted the same strange disease
as those in the mines.

33:06.070 --> 33:07.350
They ate the rations
issued by the imperial court

33:07.350 --> 33:09.030
that had been soaked
in contaminated water.

33:09.030 --> 33:11.090
And those rations came from Guazhou.

33:11.510 --> 33:14.240
Someone must have learned
the secret about Guazhou

33:14.240 --> 33:16.000
and dragged the Beifu soldiers into this

33:16.000 --> 33:17.600
just in order to lure me here.

33:18.070 --> 33:19.590
It can not only deal a blow
to the Beifu Reform

33:19.590 --> 33:21.270
but also destroy the Cui family.

33:21.270 --> 33:22.930
I guess the person behind this

33:24.640 --> 33:25.480
is the Grand Tutor.

33:25.480 --> 33:26.240
My father?

33:26.960 --> 33:28.820
The Grand Tutor and the Cui family

33:29.070 --> 33:30.600
probably have a blood feud.

33:32.720 --> 33:34.000
Judging from the time,

33:35.480 --> 33:36.480
Li Mao must have

33:37.070 --> 33:39.200
raided the Cui Mansion in Jiankang by now.

33:39.200 --> 33:41.150
The people he dispatched from Jiankang

33:41.150 --> 33:42.310
should arrive in a few days.

33:42.310 --> 33:44.440
You... Why didn't you tell me earlier?

33:44.480 --> 33:45.720
You guys, go there.

33:45.830 --> 33:46.430
-Understood!
-Understood!

33:46.430 --> 33:46.990
And you.

33:47.270 --> 33:48.750
They are locked up in the cell ahead.

33:48.750 --> 33:49.480
Understood.

33:49.640 --> 33:50.840
What is he doing here?

33:53.030 --> 33:54.290
Sealing off the mines.

33:56.200 --> 33:57.130
Don't be afraid.

34:00.960 --> 34:02.340
According to my master's order,

34:02.340 --> 34:03.720
you two are distinguished guests,

34:03.720 --> 34:05.440
and the path
to the afterlife is a painful one.

34:05.440 --> 34:07.170
If you want to die a quick death,

34:07.270 --> 34:08.360
you can take this poison.

34:08.360 --> 34:09.510
It seems that Cui Jun

34:09.880 --> 34:11.360
really wants me dead.

34:15.190 --> 34:16.000
Master!

34:23.340 --> 34:23.900
Master.

34:25.320 --> 34:26.590
Where have you been the past few days?

34:26.590 --> 34:29.110
I don't even want to bring it up.
You wouldn't believe me.

34:29.110 --> 34:30.110
The past few days,

34:30.350 --> 34:33.310
I've been eating well
for all 3 meals every day.

34:33.550 --> 34:34.929
Except for that mute
who delivered the food,

34:34.929 --> 34:36.110
I didn't see anyone else.

34:36.110 --> 34:36.590
Wait,

34:36.710 --> 34:37.980
w-why? There's no way!

34:38.030 --> 34:39.030
Look...

34:40.280 --> 34:41.070
Hurry.

34:41.280 --> 34:42.190
Sorry.

34:44.110 --> 34:45.840
Where are Qing Long and Yan Yue?

34:47.590 --> 34:49.190
You were not led here by them?

34:49.230 --> 34:49.840
No.

34:52.440 --> 34:53.630
It was Cui Shao'an.

35:12.880 --> 35:14.610
The mines in the back mountain.

35:17.150 --> 35:19.920
The Cui family is grateful
for His Majesty's grace.

35:19.920 --> 35:22.440
I am willing to be
diligent and self-disciplined,

35:22.440 --> 35:24.070
strictly follow the imperial edict,

35:24.070 --> 35:26.550
form a marriage alliance with Prince Qi,

35:26.670 --> 35:29.730
and devote my absolute loyalty
and effort to the state.

35:29.760 --> 35:31.840
I will not fail His Majesty's grace.

35:36.030 --> 35:39.670
I, Cui Lingyi, am willing
to serve Prince Qi

35:39.670 --> 35:41.800
and be of one mind and principle
with His Highness

35:41.800 --> 35:43.280
to protect our family and state,

35:43.280 --> 35:45.340
with fidelity for the rest of my life.

35:45.760 --> 35:46.670
You may rise.

35:49.030 --> 35:49.840
Wait!

35:52.960 --> 35:54.220
You rebellious child!

35:54.280 --> 35:56.150
Today is your sister's big day
of being escorted as the bride.

35:56.150 --> 35:57.360
What are you going to do?

35:57.360 --> 35:59.840
Guards! Take my unfilial son out!

36:07.110 --> 36:08.510
I, Cui Shao'an, pay my respects

36:08.510 --> 36:10.030
to you, Princess Pingning.

36:10.030 --> 36:10.840
You killed...

36:11.110 --> 36:13.170
The one I killed is not my real sister.

36:13.400 --> 36:14.400
You brat!

36:19.280 --> 36:20.010
Cui Shao'an,

36:20.920 --> 36:22.120
what did you just say?

36:22.150 --> 36:23.550
My sister, Cui Lingyi,

36:24.110 --> 36:26.510
was killed by my father long ago,

36:26.880 --> 36:28.880
with her body destroyed overnight.

36:29.480 --> 36:30.810
If you don't believe me,

36:31.550 --> 36:34.150
Your Highness,
here is my sister's handwritten letter

36:34.150 --> 36:36.670
as well as the evidence
of the crimes that my Cui family

36:36.670 --> 36:38.350
has committed over the past 20 years,

36:38.350 --> 36:40.400
which my sister left behind
at the price of her life!

36:40.400 --> 36:42.330
Please take a look, Your Highness!

36:58.110 --> 37:00.630
What are these bloody contracts?

37:01.280 --> 37:03.760
Cui Jun, you've not only
run illegal private mines

37:03.760 --> 37:05.150
but also harmed young girls and children

37:05.150 --> 37:06.400
and made them mine for you,

37:06.400 --> 37:08.330
causing countless unjust deaths.

37:08.360 --> 37:10.920
Do you even care about
the imperial court and the people?

37:10.920 --> 37:13.280
How can you claim to stand with Prince Qi

37:13.480 --> 37:14.630
in protecting the state

37:14.630 --> 37:16.360
and carrying out a great cause?

37:16.920 --> 37:17.670
Guards!

37:22.000 --> 37:25.360
Your Highness, you came to Lingfeng Fort
with the armed Imperial Guards

37:25.360 --> 37:27.460
under the guise of escorting the bride.

37:27.460 --> 37:30.350
What are you up to?

37:33.440 --> 37:35.630
Cui Jun, are you trying to rebel?

37:35.840 --> 37:36.880
Listen up, guys.

37:37.480 --> 37:39.140
Whoever kills Li Lejun will be

37:39.200 --> 37:43.200
rewarded with 1,000 households'
tax revenues and 10,000 taels of gold!

37:59.400 --> 38:00.000
Brother!

38:00.880 --> 38:01.440
Sister!

38:03.920 --> 38:04.480
Brother!

38:06.760 --> 38:07.400
Brother!

38:11.840 --> 38:13.170
Kill them, and you'll be

38:13.190 --> 38:14.650
rewarded based on merits!

38:16.550 --> 38:17.880
Who dares to make a move?

38:22.400 --> 38:23.930
We're standing here today.

38:24.280 --> 38:25.480
You can make your move

38:25.590 --> 38:26.880
and kill all of us!

38:27.590 --> 38:28.920
But look at these faces.

38:29.150 --> 38:30.320
Are they any different

38:30.320 --> 38:31.650
from your own families?

38:33.400 --> 38:34.790
If you raise your blades to kill us today,

38:34.790 --> 38:36.590
someone will use the same blades

38:36.590 --> 38:38.520
to murder your families tomorrow!

38:59.190 --> 39:00.510
Bring her here!

39:02.760 --> 39:03.400
Mother!

39:04.840 --> 39:06.190
Xie Jiayu, Xiao Wuyi,

39:06.800 --> 39:08.230
if you take one more step forward,

39:08.230 --> 39:09.320
I'll have Yunzhao

39:09.550 --> 39:11.230
die in front of you right away.

39:11.480 --> 39:12.280
Cui Jun,

39:13.440 --> 39:14.510
don't you dare.

39:21.800 --> 39:23.110
Xiao Wuyi, you...

39:23.510 --> 39:25.370
This is the Beifu Army's war drum.

39:25.760 --> 39:26.710
Xiao Wuyi,

39:27.360 --> 39:28.960
when did you set this up?

39:31.030 --> 39:32.750
Since the moment Princess Yunzhao told you

39:32.750 --> 39:35.010
the Phoenix Heart Token's whereabouts.

39:45.590 --> 39:46.650
Qing Long, Yan Yue!

40:02.670 --> 40:04.800
This is the totem
of Northern Qin's Eagle King.

40:04.800 --> 40:07.200
Yes, they are all
the Eagle King's henchmen

40:07.550 --> 40:08.840
from Northern Qin.

40:09.000 --> 40:09.670
Cui Jun,

40:10.460 --> 40:13.440
the Eagle King of Northern Qin is
the client of your private mines.

40:13.440 --> 40:16.110
You have been colluding
with Northern Qin all along.

40:16.110 --> 40:17.710
How audacious you are.

40:19.880 --> 40:20.630
Cui Jun,

40:21.550 --> 40:22.710
over 20 years ago,

40:22.910 --> 40:24.800
when Northern Qin attacked the Capital,

40:24.800 --> 40:25.510
you were accusing

40:25.510 --> 40:27.400
the An and Lu families for the first time.

40:27.400 --> 40:31.260
Could it be that you had already colluded
with Northern Qin back then,

40:31.510 --> 40:34.110
causing the horrible bloodshed
in the Capital?

40:34.110 --> 40:35.570
What horrible bloodshed?

40:36.230 --> 40:39.880
I only know that the Ans and Lus conspired
with the enemy and committed treason.

40:39.880 --> 40:42.360
I only know that Emperor Wenxi was
licentious and brutal,

40:42.360 --> 40:44.590
bringing destruction
to the state and families.

40:44.590 --> 40:45.360
How dare you!

40:46.280 --> 40:48.410
How dare you slander the late Emperor?

40:48.730 --> 40:49.730
Don't forget that

40:49.950 --> 40:51.750
you are Empress Wenxi's brother

40:52.360 --> 40:54.360
and the Phoenix Heart Token holder,

40:54.440 --> 40:56.070
bearing the responsibility
of moving Ye south

40:56.070 --> 40:57.190
and assisting Crown Prince Wenxi...

40:57.190 --> 40:59.050
Crown Prince Wenxi died long ago!

40:59.050 --> 41:00.070
He is not dead!

41:03.110 --> 41:04.840
Crown Prince Wenxi is not dead?

41:07.630 --> 41:08.400
Tell me.

41:09.840 --> 41:11.360
Who is Crown Prince Wenxi?

41:11.840 --> 41:12.900
Where is he hiding?

41:24.900 --> 41:25.590
Mother!

41:31.760 --> 41:32.280
Mother.

41:33.510 --> 41:34.240
Are you okay?

41:34.270 --> 41:34.790
I'm fine.
